Dialogue: 15,0:00:13.16,0:00:16.36,Youkoso,ishizaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}Deja de inventar rumores,\NHashimoto.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:16.36,0:00:20.54,Youkoso,ibuki,0,0,0,,{\be2}Sabemos que los difundes\Nporque Sakayanagi te lo ordena.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.86,Youkoso,shiina,0,0,0,,{\be2}Detente, por favor, Ibuki.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:22.86,0:00:24.62,Youkoso,ibuki,0,0,0,,{\be2}Tú no te metas.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:24.88,0:00:27.66,Youkoso,ishizaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}No creas que no habrá consecuencias.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.74,Youkoso,hashimoto,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿De verdad quieren pelear?
Dialogue: 15,0:00:30.13,0:00:31.55,Youkoso,yukimura,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡No lo hagan!
Dialogue: 15,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.47,Youkoso,miyake,0,0,0,,{\be2}Cálmense.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.50,Youkoso,ishizaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡No es asunto suyo!
Dialogue: 15,0:00:34.51,0:00:37.85,Youkoso,yukimura,0,0,0,,{\be2}También hay rumores sobre Ayanokoji.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:37.85,0:00:39.00,Youkoso,yukimura,0,0,0,,{\be2}Igual nos concierne.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:39.00,0:00:42.39,Youkoso,hashimoto,0,0,0,,{\be2}Que digan que te gusta\NKaruizawa es encantador.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:43.19,0:00:45.64,Youkoso,sakura,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡N-No es para nada encantador!
Dialogue: 15,0:00:45.98,0:00:48.90,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Odio tener que decir esto,
Dialogue: 15,0:00:48.90,0:00:52.20,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}pero yo también sospecho\Nde ti, Hashimoto.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:52.20,0:00:53.65,Youkoso,hashimoto,0,0,0,,{\be2}Era de esperarse.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:53.65,0:00:57.53,Youkoso,hashimoto,0,0,0,,{\be2}Fui el único que te vio reunirte\Ncon Karuizawa en secreto.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:57.53,0:00:59.02,Youkoso,sakura/hasebe,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿"En secreto"?
Dialogue: 15,0:00:59.02,0:01:01.29,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}No hay nada entre nosotros.
Dialogue: 15,0:01:02.04,0:01:04.50,Youkoso,ishizaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡Deja de ignorarme!
Dialogue: 15,0:01:04.50,0:01:05.50,Youkoso,shiina,0,0,0,,{\be2}Ishizaki,
Dialogue: 15,0:01:05.50,0:01:06.78,Youkoso,shiina,0,0,0,,{\be2}no permitiré que sigas.
Dialogue: 15,0:01:06.78,0:01:08.34,Youkoso,ishizaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}Pero…
Dialogue: 15,0:01:08.34,0:01:10.38,Youkoso,shiina,0,0,0,,{\be2}Aunque lo obligaras a confesar,
Dialogue: 15,0:01:10.38,0:01:13.04,Youkoso,shiina,0,0,0,,{\be2}Sakayanagi no admitiría\Nnada en absoluto.
Dialogue: 15,0:01:13.04,0:01:14.94,Youkoso,ibuki,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Esperas a que nos lo traguemos?
Dialogue: 15,0:01:16.10,0:01:19.81,Youkoso,shiina,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Podrías perdonarnos por lo de hoy?
Dialogue: 15,0:01:19.81,0:01:23.27,Youkoso,hashimoto,0,0,0,,{\be2}Bueno, no es como si estuviera herido.
Dialogue: 15,0:01:23.81,0:01:28.31,Youkoso,hashimoto,0,0,0,,{\be2}Pero ya dejen de dudar\Ny acusarme imprudentemente.
Dialogue: 15,0:01:28.69,0:01:31.38,Youkoso,hashimoto,0,0,0,,{\be2}No quiero problemas si no hay pruebas.
Dialogue: 15,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.58,Youkoso,shiina,0,0,0,,{\be2}De acuerdo.
Dialogue: 15,0:01:34.70,0:01:35.95,Youkoso,shiina,0,0,0,,{\be2}Vámonos.
Dialogue: 15,0:01:49.09,0:01:53.34,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8\be2}Ichinose por fin regresó.
Dialogue: 15,0:01:53.34,0:01:56.60,Youkoso,kamuro,0,0,0,,{\be2}Justo a tiempo para los exámenes.
Dialogue: 15,0:01:56.60,0:01:57.43,Youkoso,kamuro,0,0,0,,{\be2}Dime,
Dialogue: 15,0:01:57.43,0:01:58.81,Youkoso,kamuro,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿qué haremos?
Dialogue: 15,0:02:04.19,0:02:05.36,Youkoso,yukimura,0,0,0,,{\be2}Muy bien.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:05.90,0:02:07.86,Youkoso,yukimura,0,0,0,,{\be2}Son buenos resultados.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:09.03,0:02:09.78,Youkoso,hasebe,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡Wow!
Dialogue: 15,0:02:09.78,0:02:11.65,Youkoso,hasebe,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡{\i1}Kiyopon{\i0}, tienes 90!
Dialogue: 15,0:02:11.65,0:02:12.74,Youkoso,hasebe,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡Increíble!
Dialogue: 15,0:02:12.74,0:02:13.99,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Pero ustedes
Dialogue: 15,0:02:13.99,0:02:16.00,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}no se quedan atrás.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:17.33,0:02:18.50,Youkoso,ike,0,0,0,,{\an8\be2}¡Oigan!
Dialogue: 15,0:02:18.50,0:02:22.00,Youkoso,ike,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡Un grupo de la clase A\Nacaba de llegar a la clase B!
Dialogue: 15,0:02:28.25,0:02:31.00,Youkoso,amikura,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Qué haces aquí, Sakayanagi?
Dialogue: 15,0:02:32.17,0:02:33.51,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Siempre he admirado
Dialogue: 15,0:02:33.51,0:02:37.75,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}cómo la clase B trabaja en equipo.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:37.75,0:02:39.39,Youkoso,amikura,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Qué quieres decir?
Dialogue: 15,0:02:40.72,0:02:44.39,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}He venido a salvarlos.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:45.19,0:02:47.65,Youkoso,kanzaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿A dónde quieres llegar?
Dialogue: 15,0:02:47.65,0:02:51.40,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Sé que es cierto que le dan sus\Npuntos privados a Ichinose
Dialogue: 15,0:02:51.40,0:02:55.74,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}y que han superado muchas\Ndificultades gracias a esos ahorros.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:55.74,0:02:57.65,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}He venido a hablarles de eso.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.78,Youkoso,kanzaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Hay algún problema con eso?
Dialogue: 15,0:02:59.78,0:03:03.28,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Ya se anunció que\Nno es ningún crimen.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:05.42,0:03:06.71,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Aun así,
Dialogue: 15,0:03:06.71,0:03:11.55,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿y si las acusaciones fueran ciertas?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:11.55,0:03:15.43,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Y si Ichinose\Nrealmente fuera una criminal?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:15.43,0:03:16.97,Youkoso,kanzaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}Es mentira.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:16.97,0:03:20.47,Youkoso,kanzaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}Al igual que todos\Nlos rumores que difunden.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:20.47,0:03:23.93,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Esos a mí no me conciernen.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.48,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Lo que tengo aquí
Dialogue: 15,0:03:26.48,0:03:30.69,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}son pruebas sobre\Nlos rumores de Ichinose.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.44,Youkoso,estudiantes,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Pruebas?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.44,Youkoso,estudiantes,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Qué quiere decir?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.70,Youkoso,amikura,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡Cálmense todos!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:36.70,0:03:40.78,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Darle sus puntos de privados\Na una persona así,
Dialogue: 15,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.19,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿no los llevará a la ruina?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:44.25,0:03:47.21,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿O estoy equivocada,
Dialogue: 15,0:03:47.75,0:03:49.88,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Honami Ichinose?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.67,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Podrían dejarme pasar?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.13,Youkoso,kanzaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Ichinose?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:57.15,0:03:58.72,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}No te procupes.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.60,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Lo siento, chicos.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.57,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Guarden silencio.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:15.57,0:04:18.49,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Está a punto de confesar sus pecados.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:21.45,0:04:22.49,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Chicos.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:23.37,0:04:27.24,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Creen que puedan escuchar\Nlo que tengo que decir?
Dialogue: 15,0:04:28.66,0:04:31.25,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Sakayanagi tiene razón.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.49,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Cometí un crimen.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.01,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Un crimen imperdonable.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.39,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Antes
Dialogue: 15,0:04:47.39,0:04:51.77,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}vivía con mi mamá\Ny mi hermana dos años menor.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.90,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Aunque no éramos\Nmuy adineradas,
Dialogue: 15,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.40,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}siempre fuimos felices.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:59.45,0:05:05.91,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Mi mamá se esforzaba muchísimo\Npor nosotras.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:13.71,0:05:18.05,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Por eso intenté conseguir una beca\Npara poder seguir estudiando
Dialogue: 15,0:05:18.05,0:05:21.38,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}pese a que no podíamos pagarlo.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.10,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Pero…
Dialogue: 15,0:05:32.98,0:05:35.94,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}durante el verano de tercero de secundaria…
Dialogue: 15,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.78,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}mi mamá…
Dialogue: 15,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.49,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}enfermó.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:49.04,0:05:52.54,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Venía el cumpleaños de mi hermana\Ny ella quería darle algo.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.08,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Entonces asumió\Nmás turnos en el trabajo.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:57.55,0:06:00.63,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}A mi hermana le encantaba una idol.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:01.80,0:06:04.84,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Y nos había dicho\Nque quería su mismo fijador.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.14,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Mi hermana
Dialogue: 15,0:06:08.14,0:06:12.14,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}siempre se había abstenido\Nde pedir ropa o juegos.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:13.14,0:06:17.86,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Eso fue lo primero que nos pidió.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.57,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Mi mamá le decía:
Dialogue: 15,0:06:25.57,0:06:28.95,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}"Siento no poder darte\Nun regalo de cumpleaños".
Dialogue: 15,0:06:28.95,0:06:32.87,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Mi mamá le repitió mil\Ny un veces que lo sentía.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:34.75,0:06:36.88,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Ahí fue cuando tomé una decisión.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.92,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Sin importar lo que costara,
Dialogue: 15,0:06:38.92,0:06:42.38,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}yo compraría el fijador\Npara mi hermana.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:47.05,0:06:48.85,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Yo era conciente
Dialogue: 15,0:06:48.85,0:06:52.68,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}de que era difícil,\Ncomo estudiante de secundaria,
Dialogue: 15,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.48,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}reunir dinero.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.61,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Aun así,
Dialogue: 15,0:06:58.61,0:07:01.03,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}reuní todo el que pude.
Dialogue: 15,0:07:02.03,0:07:03.16,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Pero…
Dialogue: 15,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.34,Youkoso,colegiala 1,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8\be2}Qué bonita es.
Dialogue: 15,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.33,Youkoso,colegiala 2,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8\be2}Es la de la revista.
Dialogue: 15,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.84,Youkoso,colegiala 1,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Sí, lo quiero.
Dialogue: 15,0:07:23.26,0:07:24.80,Youkoso,colegiala 2,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Está genial.
Dialogue: 15,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.42,Youkoso,colegiala 2,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}¿Volvemos mañana?
Dialogue: 15,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.85,Youkoso,colegiala 1,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Sí, porque hoy no nos alcanza…
Dialogue: 15,0:07:38.81,0:07:43.61,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Quería el fijador a como diera lugar.
Dialogue: 15,0:07:57.71,0:08:00.00,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Nadie me vio tomarlo.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.92,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Le mentí diciéndole
Dialogue: 15,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.09,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}que me...
Dialogue: 15,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.18,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}lo había dado una amiga.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:10.93,0:08:13.93,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Mi hermana estaba demasiado feliz.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:14.43,0:08:18.39,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Me dio las gracias una y otra vez.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.52,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Al verla sonreír,
Dialogue: 15,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.36,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}mi sentimiento de culpa
Dialogue: 15,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.36,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}se desvaneció por un momento.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.87,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}El día que mi mamá dejó el hospital,
Dialogue: 15,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.58,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}fuimos a buscarla juntas.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:34.99,0:08:40.04,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Mi hermana le enseñó\Nel fijador llena de orgullo.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:41.04,0:08:45.21,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}No podía pedirle\Nque lo mantuviera en secreto.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.84,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}No con lo contenta que estaba.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.22,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Mi mamá
Dialogue: 15,0:08:55.77,0:08:59.19,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}se dio cuenta de que la había robado.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:59.19,0:09:01.23,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}No pude ocultárselo.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:03.86,0:09:08.61,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Enseguida me llevó a la tienda\Npara que me disculpara.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:08.99,0:09:12.62,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Ahí fue cuando por fin asimilé
Dialogue: 15,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.07,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}lo que había hecho.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.88,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Al volver a casa,
Dialogue: 15,0:09:17.88,0:09:21.08,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}mi mamá se puso a llorar desconsoladamente.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.88,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Era la primera vez
Dialogue: 15,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.98,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}que la veía llorar de verdad.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:29.67,0:09:35.35,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Al final, la tienda\Nno me denunció a la policía.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:36.85,0:09:39.56,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Pero yo me encerré en mí misma.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:39.56,0:09:40.89,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Durante medio año
Dialogue: 15,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.06,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}me culpé por lo que había pasado
Dialogue: 15,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.40,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}y me encerré en mi habitación.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:08.59,0:10:12.55,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Pero mi mamá me dijo…
Dialogue: 15,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.64,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}que tenía que seguir estudiando.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:20.10,0:10:23.94,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Que quería que alcanzara\Nmi propia felicidad.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.41,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Por eso,
Dialogue: 15,0:10:39.08,0:10:42.29,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,decidí empezar de nuevo\Nen esta escuela.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:43.08,0:10:50.30,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1235)\i1\be2}Para recuperar la confianza\Nde mi mamá y mi hermana.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.05,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Chicos,
Dialogue: 15,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.84,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}siento no habérselos dicho antes.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:57.93,0:11:02.27,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Lamento ser una líder tan patética e inútil.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.61,Youkoso,shibata,0,0,0,,{\be2}Eso no es verdad, Ichinose.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:05.60,0:11:08.06,Youkoso,kanzaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}Lo entiendo.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.82,Youkoso,amikura,0,0,0,,{\be2}Nos revelaste tu secreto
Dialogue: 15,0:11:09.82,0:11:13.62,Youkoso,amikura,0,0,0,,{\be2}porque confías en nosotros, ¿no?
Dialogue: 15,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.60,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Chicos…
Dialogue: 15,0:11:18.03,0:11:20.58,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Dejen de ser tan ridículos.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.59,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Sakayanagi…
Dialogue: 15,0:11:22.95,0:11:26.46,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}No importan las circunstancias,\Nrobar sigue siendo robar.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:27.00,0:11:29.36,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2} No hay lugar para\Nque te compadezcan.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.85,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Tienes... razón.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:33.38,0:11:37.47,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}El crimen que cometí nunca desaparecerá.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:37.47,0:11:38.80,Youkoso,kanzaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}Ichinose…
Dialogue: 15,0:11:39.22,0:11:42.72,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Es cierto que un crimen es un crimen,
Dialogue: 15,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.98,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}pero no voy a huir de eso.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.10,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Porque
Dialogue: 15,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.98,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}lo que hice estuvo mal.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:51.36,0:11:55.07,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}No tienes ni escrúpulos ni vergüenza.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:55.07,0:11:56.45,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}No.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:56.45,0:12:00.41,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Tal vez mis esfuerzos sean hipócritas,
Dialogue: 15,0:12:01.49,0:12:06.87,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}pero quiero graduarme con esta clase.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:06.87,0:12:09.50,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Quiero subir junto a ustedes.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:10.13,0:12:12.09,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Sabiendo cómo soy,
Dialogue: 15,0:12:12.09,0:12:16.01,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿me seguirán hasta el final?
Dialogue: 15,0:12:16.01,0:12:17.26,Youkoso,kanzaki,0,0,0,,{\be2}Por supuesto.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:17.51,0:12:19.55,Youkoso,shibata,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡Claro que te seguiremos!
Dialogue: 15,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.05,Youkoso,estudiantes,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡Por supuesto!
Dialogue: 15,0:12:21.05,0:12:21.85,Youkoso,estudiantes,0,0,0,,{\be2}Sí.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:21.85,0:12:22.64,Youkoso,estudiantes,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡Claro que sí!
Dialogue: 15,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.39,Youkoso,yukimura,0,0,0,,{\be2}Qué increíble.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.23,Youkoso,kamuro,0,0,0,,{\be2}Sakayanagi,
Dialogue: 15,0:12:30.23,0:12:31.48,Youkoso,kamuro,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿y ahora qué?
Dialogue: 15,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.15,Youkoso,kamuro,0,0,0,,{\be2}Oye, te estoy hablando.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.86,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Ya veo.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:37.86,0:12:40.16,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Los tienes comiendo de tu mano.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:40.91,0:12:45.16,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Pero eres una criminal\Ny eso es un hecho.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:45.16,0:12:48.21,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Los rumores \Nseguirán circulando.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.92,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Pero ya no voy a huir.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.83,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Es eso cierto?
Dialogue: 15,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.50,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}En ese caso…
Dialogue: 15,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.67,Youkoso,nagumo,0,0,0,,{\be2}Bueno, chicas,
Dialogue: 15,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.21,Youkoso,nagumo,0,0,0,,{\be2}es suficiente.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.80,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Presidente del consejo,
Dialogue: 15,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.80,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}profesores.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.39,Youkoso,nagumo,0,0,0,,{\be2}Desde hoy queda prohibido
Dialogue: 15,0:13:01.39,0:13:04.44,Youkoso,nagumo,0,0,0,,{\be2}difundir rumores malintencionados.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:04.43,0:13:07.85,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Acaso Ichinose reportó en persona
Dialogue: 15,0:13:07.85,0:13:10.44,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}el problema que estaba teniendo?
Dialogue: 15,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.23,Youkoso,nagumo,0,0,0,,{\be2}El problema ya no solo
Dialogue: 15,0:13:12.23,0:13:14.90,Youkoso,nagumo,0,0,0,,{\be2}se centra en Ichinose.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.94,Youkoso,mashima,0,0,0,,{\be2}Entre los de primero
Dialogue: 15,0:13:16.94,0:13:20.83,Youkoso,mashima,0,0,0,,{\be2}estaban difundiéndose\Ncalumnias abusivas.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:21.41,0:13:25.66,Youkoso,hoshinomiya,0,0,0,,{\be2}Esta práctica afectará\Na la disciplina de la escuela.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.91,Youkoso,hoshinomiya,0,0,0,,{\be2}Se aplicará un castigo
Dialogue: 15,0:13:28.91,0:13:32.09,Youkoso,hoshinomiya,0,0,0,,{\be2}a aquellos que difundan\Nrumores malintencionados.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:33.92,0:13:35.50,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Comprendo.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:35.50,0:13:39.67,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Si la escuela interviene,\Nno hace falta que me quede.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.13,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Hora de irnos.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:54.19,0:13:55.86,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Bien jugado,
Dialogue: 15,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.94,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Ayanokoji.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:58.57,0:14:01.11,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Dime una cosa.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:01.49,0:14:07.24,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Ichinose te confesó\Nlo que había hecho, ¿no?
Dialogue: 15,0:14:07.84,0:14:08.97,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Sí.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:12.16,0:14:16.04,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}Ayer fui a visitar a\NIchinose en su habitación.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.80,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Oye,
Dialogue: 15,0:14:20.80,0:14:23.51,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}¿puedo preguntarte algo?
Dialogue: 15,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.43,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Sí.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:25.43,0:14:30.14,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}¿Por qué no me has dicho\No preguntado nada?
Dialogue: 15,0:14:32.18,0:14:35.02,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Vengo todos los días
Dialogue: 15,0:14:35.02,0:14:38.27,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}porque estoy esperando\N que me lo cuentes todo.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:39.61,0:14:40.94,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}O eso creo.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:42.11,0:14:45.20,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}¿Esperas... que confiese?
Dialogue: 15,0:14:45.86,0:14:50.70,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Conozco el crimen\Nque cometiste en el pasado.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.71,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Ichinose,
Dialogue: 15,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.46,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}huir no hará desaparecer\Nlo que hiciste.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:57.46,0:14:58.84,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}¡Para!
Dialogue: 15,0:15:00.38,0:15:02.55,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Yo sé…
Dialogue: 15,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.88,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Yo sé que…
Dialogue: 15,0:15:04.17,0:15:07.05,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Sé que lo que hice estuvo mal.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:07.43,0:15:11.68,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Pero entonces creía\Nque no tenía otra opción.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.52,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}A mi hermana...
Dialogue: 15,0:15:14.52,0:15:16.69,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Quería hacerla feliz...
Dialogue: 15,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.27,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}No lo pensé.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.78,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Fui una tonta.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:21.78,0:15:24.11,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Solo pensé en huir.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.95,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}¡Como ahora!
Dialogue: 15,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.37,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Como ahora.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:32.12,0:15:36.50,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Volví a encerrarme en mí misma.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:38.04,0:15:40.75,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}¿Qué debí haber hecho?
Dialogue: 15,0:15:41.46,0:15:43.38,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}¿Qué debí hacer?
Dialogue: 15,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.72,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Dime.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:45.42,0:15:48.43,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Dime, Ayanokoji.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:49.43,0:15:53.85,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}¿Qué tengo que hacer\Npara salir de este cuarto?
Dialogue: 15,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.77,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}No lo sé.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.77,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Tienes que afrontarlo tú misma.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.02,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}¿No es así?
Dialogue: 15,0:16:07.74,0:16:10.20,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}A Ichinose se le rompió el corazón.
Dialogue: 15,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.65,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Pero yo…
Dialogue: 15,0:16:20.13,0:16:21.25,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Yo…
Dialogue: 15,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.16,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}se lo hice pedazos.
Dialogue: 15,0:16:27.05,0:16:31.47,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Así, los pedazos se regeneraron\Ncon mucha más fuerza
Dialogue: 15,0:16:31.47,0:16:33.89,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}y resistieron tus acusaciones.
Dialogue: 15,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.35,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Eso es todo.
Dialogue: 15,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.56,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Qué conmovedor.
Dialogue: 15,0:16:38.94,0:16:42.31,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Pero tú usaste a Kamuro\Npara obligarme a actuar.
Dialogue: 15,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.82,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Qué te hace estar tan seguro?
Dialogue: 15,0:16:45.36,0:16:48.32,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}La lata de cerveza que me dio Kamuro
Dialogue: 15,0:16:48.32,0:16:51.28,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}la robó al inicio del año escolar.
Dialogue: 15,0:16:51.70,0:16:54.58,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}La fecha de caducidad de la lata
Dialogue: 15,0:16:54.58,0:16:57.66,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}era casi un año más antigua
Dialogue: 15,0:16:57.66,0:17:00.00,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1\be2}que la de las que venden ahora.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:01.29,0:17:06.59,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Por lo tanto, la lata\Nvenía de ti, Sakayanagi.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:08.80,0:17:12.97,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}No tenía planeado\Nintervenir en este incidente.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:13.51,0:17:17.10,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Pero me involucraste usando a Kamuro.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.22,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Por qué?
Dialogue: 15,0:17:18.22,0:17:22.69,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Para que yo llamara tu atención.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:22.69,0:17:27.90,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Así que Ichinose\Nno te importaba en lo más mínimo.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.74,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Así es.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:30.95,0:17:33.12,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Hagamos una competencia.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.75,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Yo no gano nada.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:35.75,0:17:38.25,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Y si digo que apuesto
Dialogue: 15,0:17:38.25,0:17:41.00,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}mi permanencia en la escuela?
Dialogue: 15,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.00,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Por supuesto,
Dialogue: 15,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.63,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}aunque pierdas,
Dialogue: 15,0:17:44.63,0:17:47.50,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}no te pediré que dejes la escuela.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.76,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Sin embargo,
Dialogue: 15,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.13,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}si pierdes,
Dialogue: 15,0:17:51.13,0:17:55.27,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}revelaré que eres quien lidera\Nla clase C desde las sombras.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.02,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Qué se considerará ganar?
Dialogue: 15,0:17:58.02,0:18:00.64,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Compitamos en el próximo examen.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.52,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}Con esto, por fin,
Dialogue: 15,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.64,Youkoso,sakayanagi,0,0,0,,{\be2}mi aburrida vida escolar\Nllegará a su fin.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:14.66,0:18:17.41,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Gracias por los chocolates.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:18.54,0:18:23.67,Youkoso,kushida,0,0,0,,{\be2}No te llamé para hablar de eso.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:24.29,0:18:28.92,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}La información que Kushida\Nme dio antes de San Valentín
Dialogue: 15,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.51,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}era acertada.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:31.76,0:18:34.01,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Vicepresidente Kiriyama,
Dialogue: 15,0:18:34.01,0:18:37.68,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}necesito que publique esto en los foros.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.93,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Es para salvar a Ichinose.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:39.93,0:18:44.31,Youkoso,kiriyama,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Si me descubrieran,\Nel consejo perdería credibilidad.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:44.31,0:18:45.77,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Si así fuera,
Dialogue: 15,0:18:45.77,0:18:49.27,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}el presidente Nagumo\Nse llevaría todo el daño.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:49.94,0:18:52.69,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Yo digo que es positivo\Npor donde lo veas.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:52.69,0:18:56.03,Youkoso,kiriyama,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Yo sería penalizado por la escuela.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.66,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Si te niegas,
Dialogue: 15,0:18:59.20,0:19:02.71,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}tendré que informarle\Nal anterior presidente
Dialogue: 15,0:19:03.08,0:19:06.71,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}que ahora estás del lado de Nagumo.
Dialogue: 15,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.54,Youkoso,kiriyama,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Muy bien.
Dialogue: 15,0:19:08.54,0:19:12.46,Youkoso,kiriyama,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Me debes un favor de los grandes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.47,Youkoso,kushida,0,0,0,,Gracias.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:18.10,Youkoso,kushida,0,0,0,,Me alegro de serte útil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:20.14,Youkoso,kushida,0,0,0,,Bueno, ya sabes qué sigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:20.84,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.48,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Ya hice la transferencia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.31,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Compruébalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.48,Youkoso,kushida,0,0,0,,Perfecto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:34.99,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Seguiré cediéndote\Nla mitad de los puntos que gane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.99,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,¿Te parece?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:38.97,Youkoso,kushida,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:41.20,Youkoso,kushida,0,0,0,,Mientras me pagues,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.75,Youkoso,kushida,0,0,0,,no me enemistaré contigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:46.00,Youkoso,kushida,0,0,0,,Eres increíble, Ayanokoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:48.75,Youkoso,kushida,0,0,0,,Nada que ver con Horikita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.63,Youkoso,kushida,0,0,0,,Seguiremos trabajando juntos, ¿no?
Dialogue: 15,0:19:52.48,0:19:55.47,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Aceptar la provocación de Sakayanagi
Dialogue: 15,0:19:55.47,0:19:57.55,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}y salvar a Ichinose
Dialogue: 15,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.26,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}solo son piezas de un tablero.
Dialogue: 15,0:19:59.80,0:20:04.52,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Solamente había una cosa\Nque quería comprobar:
Dialogue: 15,0:20:05.06,0:20:09.27,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}la cantidad y calidad de la información\Nque posee Kikyou Kushida.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:09.98,0:20:11.86,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Todo esto para lograr
Dialogue: 15,0:20:13.61,0:20:16.28,Youkoso Mind,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}expulsarla de la escuela.
Dialogue: 15,0:21:49.87,0:21:52.08,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}¡Buenos días, Ayanokoji!
Dialogue: 15,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.29,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Buenos días.
Dialogue: 15,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.55,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Ayer estuviste genial.
Dialogue: 15,0:21:57.80,0:22:00.01,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿E-Eso crees?
Dialogue: 15,0:22:00.01,0:22:03.80,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Solo uno mismo puede triunfar\N contra su pasado.
Dialogue: 15,0:22:04.47,0:22:05.93,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Es verdad.
Dialogue: 15,0:22:06.64,0:22:09.72,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}No puedo borrar lo que hice.
Dialogue: 15,0:22:09.72,0:22:13.69,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Pero puedo vivir afrontándolo.
Dialogue: 15,0:22:14.40,0:22:18.58,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Si alguna vez pierdes el rumbo de nuevo,
Dialogue: 15,0:22:19.11,0:22:21.58,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}puedes hablar conmigo.
Dialogue: 15,0:22:24.32,0:22:28.54,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Al menos puedo escucharte.
Dialogue: 15,0:22:30.33,0:22:33.50,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Puedo contar contigo?
Dialogue: 15,0:22:33.50,0:22:35.50,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}Si te sirvo de algo, sí.
Dialogue: 15,0:22:37.84,0:22:40.59,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}E-Entiendo…
Dialogue: 15,0:22:40.88,0:22:42.97,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Oye…
Dialogue: 15,0:22:43.93,0:22:45.47,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿Qué pasa?
Dialogue: 15,0:22:45.47,0:22:47.50,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Este…
Dialogue: 15,0:22:47.97,0:22:51.10,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Ay, qué raro.
Dialogue: 15,0:22:51.10,0:22:53.48,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Pretendía dártelos como si nada.
Dialogue: 15,0:22:54.31,0:23:00.28,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Verás, nunca he regalado\Nnada como esto.
Dialogue: 15,0:23:00.28,0:23:02.99,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Es la única forma\Nde expresarte mi gratitud.
Dialogue: 15,0:23:02.99,0:23:05.24,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}No tienes que forzarte\Na darme algo.
Dialogue: 15,0:23:05.24,0:23:07.87,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}No es que me sienta forzada.
Dialogue: 15,0:23:11.79,0:23:14.87,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}Es un poco tarde, pero…
Dialogue: 15,0:23:14.87,0:23:17.38,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}son chocolates de San Valentín.
Dialogue: 15,0:23:18.34,0:23:20.71,Youkoso,ichinose,0,0,0,,{\be2}¿No lo quieres?
Dialogue: 15,0:23:22.92,0:23:24.06,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}No,...
Dialogue: 15,0:23:25.01,0:23:26.09,Youkoso,ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\be2}gracias.
